name: Jsbml
tagline: JSBML is a community-driven project to create a free, open-source, pure Java library for reading, writing, and manipulating SBML files and data streams. It is an alternative to the mixed Java/native code-based interface provided in libSBML.
body:
### Welcome to the JSBML GitHub Pages.

[Go to JSBML official web site](http://sbml.org/Software/JSBML) for more information.
